// build CLI using cobra
// CLI will be supported by REST calls to controller's REST service
// For now this will be the only interface via commands/any ops can be made
// Need to go hand in hand with controller


Controller - thread  [ basically the decision maker and issuer of OPs to respective Agent ]
  e.g
  Input -
  command - launch
    template options
    number of flxc
    affinity ?

  Distribute flxc based on weight
    For now this will be a hack. Later decision will be made based on resource availability
    Allcate them at one shot

  Issue create calls to each node with count
    Set resource limits

  Get ack from agent
    update local db periodically
















